<div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q">What happens during the goods receiving inspection process?</button><div class="faq-a"><p>Every incoming shipment is quantity-checked against your packing list, visually inspected for damage, and photo-documented. Items are then barcoded (if untagged), entered into WMS with SKU data, and assigned to specific bin or pallet locations. Receiving costs from 3 UAH per unit for items under 2 kg.</p></div></div>
